text: Prignac-en-Médoc is a former commune. It is found in the region Nouvelle- Aquitaine in the Gironde department in the southwest of France. On 1 January 2019, it was merged into the new commune Blaignan-Prignac.Arrêté préfectoral 1 October 2018 == References == Category:Former communes in Gironde
title: Prignac-en-Médoc
